{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2017/august","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"directory-icons-and-program-badges\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#directory-icons-and-program-badges\" aria-label=\"directory icons and program badges permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Directory Icons and Program Badges</h3>\n<p>The Directory page now includes pink and purple lightning icons to highlight programs that are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast to respond with a first response in &#x3C;48 hours on average</li>\n<li>Fast to award by giving a bounty &#x3C;14 days after submission</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also include a <i>Managed</i> badge to identify programs that are managed by HackerOne.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 118.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sep_2017\"\n        title=\"sep_2017\"\n        src=\"/static/6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15/0b533/sep_2017.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15/fac75/sep_2017.png 125w,\n/static/6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15/63868/sep_2017.png 250w,\n/static/6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15/0b533/sep_2017.png 500w,\n/static/6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15/db783/sep_2017.png 551w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"paying-out-bounties-via-the-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#paying-out-bounties-via-the-api\" aria-label=\"paying out bounties via the api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Paying out Bounties via the API</h3>\n<p>Organizations now have the ability to payout and suggest bounties and swag using their internal systems via the API. You can view the API documentation for this <a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#reports-award-bounty\">here</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"slack-integration-20\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#slack-integration-20\" aria-label=\"slack integration 20 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Slack Integration 2.0</h3>\n<p>We've revamped our Slack integration so that programs can have:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Granular notification filtering</li>\n<li>Support for multiple channels</li>\n<li>Notifications when a username is mentioned\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"aug_2017_2\"\n        title=\"aug_2017_2\"\n        src=\"/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/0b533/aug_2017_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/fac75/aug_2017_2.png 125w,\n/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/63868/aug_2017_2.png 250w,\n/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/0b533/aug_2017_2.png 500w,\n/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/1d69c/aug_2017_2.png 750w,\n/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/00d43/aug_2017_2.png 1000w,\n/static/6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e/bd9eb/aug_2017_2.png 1442w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.hackerone.com/blog/slack-integration-update-2\">blog post</a> and learn how to <a href=\"/programs/slack-integration.html\">set up Slack integration</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bounty-splitting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bounty-splitting\" aria-label=\"bounty splitting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bounty Splitting</h3>\n<p>We now enable programs to have this feature that enables hackers to split bounties with other hackers that helped them find the vulnerability.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2017/august","title":"August 2017"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}